OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMostly cloudy with patchy rain,
OL,6,Falthough this becoming mostly confined
OL,7,Fto Argyll this afternoon. Some bright
OL,8,For sunny spells may develop across the
OL,9,Fsouth this afternoon. Very mild in any
OL,10,Fsunshine.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCentral Belt and south will
OL,13,Fhave a dry evening and night.
OL,14,FOccasional rain across Argyll, this
OL,15,Fbecoming more persistent along the
OL,16,Fwest coast later. Windy across coastal
OL,17,FArgyll.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
