OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FRain will spread east
OL,6,Fthrough the day. Becoming drier across
OL,7,FArgyll in the afternoon, and elsewhere
OL,8,Fthrough the evening.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FA cold
OL,11,Fstart with some frost on Friday, then
OL,12,Fa dry and sunny day, Dry and bright on
OL,13,FSaturday, clouding over later. Cloudy
OL,14,Fwith a chance of rain on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
